  <h2><a href="../../blog-posts/what-shale-gas-china-means-united-states" title="What Shale Gas In China Means For The United States">What Shale Gas In China Means For The United States</a></h2>

      <span class="submitted">Posted by Sarah Forbes on Jan 26, 2012</span>
  
  <div class="content clear-block">
    <div class="field field-type-filefield field-field-image">
    <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item odd">
                    <img src="../../files/chinainfo/imagecache/news-image/ShaleGas.jpg" alt="" title="" width="139" height="120" class="imagecache imagecache-news-image imagecache-default imagecache-news-image_default"/>        </div>
        </div>
</div>
<p>Today I testified before the U.S.-China Economic and Security Review Commission during a <a href="http://www.uscc.gov/hearings/2012hearings/written_testimonies/hr12_01_26.php">hearing</a> on <em>China‚Äôs Global Quest for Resources and Implications for the United States</em>. In <a href="../../library/testimony-sarah-forbes-us-china-economic-and-security-review-commission-january-26-2012">my testimony</a>, I described the prospects for shale gas in China and its implications for the United States.</p>
  </div>
<div class="clear-block">
    	<div class="readmore"> <a href="../../blog-posts/what-shale-gas-china-means-united-states">Read more</a> </div>
  </div>

  <div class="clear-block">
    <div class="meta">
        </div>

          <div class="links"><ul class="links inline"><li class="node_read_more first last"><a href="../../blog-posts/what-shale-gas-china-means-united-states" title="Read the rest of What Shale Gas In China Means For The United States.">Read more</a></li>
</ul></div>
